es who are in dire need of programs and policies aiming to end poverty<\/li>\r\n<li>The put in place on a regional, national, and international scale viable plans of action founded on development strategies favorable to the poor in order to accelerate investments targeting the elimination of poverty.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/don.breakpoverty.com\/b\/mon-don\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"You wish to help Break Poverty in its battle against poverty in the world?   (s\u2019ouvre dans un nouvel onglet)\">You wish to help Break Poverty in its battle against poverty in the world?<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><em>Credits : Ibrahim Riftah, Unsplash.<\/em><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">.<\/span><\/p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>While global poverty has declined, it remains life threatening for many people around the world where inequalities have been growing.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":25656,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[335],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v21.7 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>How to combat poverty in the world ? - Break Poverty Foundation<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"While global poverty has declined, it remains life threatening for many people around the world where inequalities have been growing.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/breakpoverty.com\/en\/how-to-combat-poverty-in-the-world\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"fr_FR\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:ti